Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:44.01,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(55,43)}第76話  「荒川即興搞笑預選賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？怎麼不是漂流台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來該輪到妮諾了  但她睡得死死的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法只好連床一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這要是掉下去了豈不是很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮諾小姐  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妮諾那傢伙  睡相還是這麼暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那是我傳授給沉睡妮諾的合氣道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？那可就是相當精彩的即興搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  是即興搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名曰  The
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡美人之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:26.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,床頭打架床尾和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  還是你那個妙欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,修女  這個怎麼讀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,史黛拉  時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  第10橋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是應該放棄交涉選擇武力啊
